data.description: Welcome to your dream home in a stunning gated neighborhood! This is a spacious and beautifully updated two-story, 5-bedroom, 2.5-bath with over 2,900 sq ft. The master bedroom located on the first floor, with BRAND NEW FLOORING, large walk in closet and double vanity! The spacious kitchen, featuring modern appliances, ample cabinet space, NEW GRANITE counter tops and a center island, perfect for entertainment. Upstairs there are four bedrooms with a large loft space. The exterior of the home is equally impressive, with a well-manicured yard that's easy to maintain. This beautiful home is not just a residence; it's a lifestyle. Located in a secure gated neighborhood, you'll have peace of mind and the added benefit of a tight-knit community. Plus, you're just moments away from parks, schools, shopping, and other conveniences.
